OL,6,FThe parents of a disabled were "blown
OL,7,Faway" when they discovered a #10,000
OL,8,Fdonation from the club's Hollywood
OL,9,Fowners to adapt their home.
OL,11,FCharlotte and Aaron Perrin's son
OL,12,FLouis, four, was born with TUBA1A,
OL,13,Fwhich is a genetic condition which
OL,14,Fmeans he has painful leg spasms,
OL,15,Flimited mobility, epilepsy and
OL,16,Fcerebral palsy.
OL,18,FHowever, he has always remained
OL,19,Fpositive and loves watching football
OL,20,Fmatches, especially when play.
