OL,6,FHis parents were "shocked" to see a
OL,7,F#10,000 donation on their fundraising
OL,8,Fpage from Ryan Reynolds and Rob
OL,9,FMcElhenney on Friday, 9 February, to
OL,10,Fhelp towards adapting their home in
OL,11,FWrexham.
OL,13,FMrs Perrin, 32, who works in the
OL,14,Femergency services, said: "Louis'
OL,15,Fcarer screenshotted the donation page
OL,16,Fand was like, 'oh my God, look at
OL,17,Fthat', and then I tried to get in
OL,18,Ftouch with my husband."
