OL,6,FMr Perrin, 32, who is a headteacher,
OL,7,Fadded: "I was at work and was sitting
OL,8,Fin the staff room and saw I had two
OL,9,Fmissed calls from Charl and then a
OL,10,Fmessage from one of my governors
OL,11,Fsaying, 'have you seen this?'
OL,13,F"I couldn't contain it. I just told
OL,14,Feveryone in work straight away.
OL,16,F"We were all amazed and so pleased and
OL,17,Fwe've had friends ringing and crying
OL,18,Fon the phone.
