OL,6,F"We were totally blown away by their
OL,7,Fgenerosity really. We were just in
OL,8,Fshock."
OL,10,FThe family are trying to #40,000 to
OL,11,Fbuild a downstairs bedroom and wet
OL,12,Froom for Louis. They also hope to make
OL,13,Fthe garden more accessible.
OL,15,F"We've gone through two sets of plans
OL,16,Fwith the local council and there has
OL,17,Fbeen no funding available due to the
OL,18,Fcost of the project, so to see the
OL,19,Fcommunity donate, it has given us more
OL,20,Fhope that we are going to achieve our
OL,21,Ftarget," Mr Perrin said.
