OL,6,FMrs Perrin added: "We just want him to
OL,7,Fbe as independent and safe as he can
OL,8,Fbe at home, and at the moment we have
OL,9,Floads of temporary equipment, which
OL,10,Fcan be a challenge as he is continuing
OL,11,Fto grow."
OL,13,FBoth Mr and Mrs Perrin spoke about how
OL,14,Fmuch joy football brings to their son.
OL,16,FMr Perrin said: "When he was a baby,
OL,17,Fhe would watch football on the TV a
OL,18,Flot and its been brilliant for me as a
OL,19,Fdad to watch him be taken in by the
OL,20,Fcolours, the noise and the cheering.
