OL,7,Fthanked Wrexham Police FC for
OL,8,Fpublicising the cause.
OL,10,F"I think it really was because of them
OL,11,Fthat Ryan and Rob got involved and it
OL,12,Fwas also so nice to see other
OL,13,Fcelebrities like Nick Knowles leave
OL,14,Fmessages of support," he added.
OL,16,F"By sharing our story, we also hope to
OL,17,Fshow that we are not a unique case.
